text: NEW: The CDC will soon shorten its guidance for quarantine periods following exposure to COVID-19.  The CDC plans to amend this to 10 days or seven with a negative test, an official told Axios. https://t.co/092yYIgi1D

text: The coronavirus was likely in the U.S. earlier than scientists initially believed — and weeks before it was officially identified in China, according to a new study by government scientists. https://t.co/81TAN0D2dz
